  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2021-03-10",
    "date": "2021-06-04T17:18:26Z",
    "text": "Measuring Real Income Growth Act of 2021\n\n This bill requires the Bureau of Economic Analysis of the Department of Commerce to include in each of its gross domestic product analyses a recent estimate of the total amount added to the U.S. economy during the period covered by the recent estimate. The estimate must also disaggregate this amount by each of the 10 deciles of income and the highest 1% of income."
  },
